data.description: Beautiful turnkey furnished home. Just bring your clothes and toothbrush! No HOA. No flood zone. Water filtration system. New HVAC 2023, roof 2020, new stainless steel appliances,  LR funiture, and updated bathrooms. The master bedroom has a huge walk-in closet adorned with a chandelier. A vaulted ceiling in the living room and pocket doors throughout the home is a plus. There is a studio on the back of the home that opens up to a large screed lanai. The yard has stone and shell with irrigation for easy care. The trees were all trimmed in 2023. This split plan home with vinyl fence is in a great location near Shamrock Park, Legacy Trail, Manasota Beach, & boat launch, restaurants and Venice shopping. The community offers a kayak/boat launch with with ferry to a private beach for a nominal fee. Enjoy the fun events at the Community Center. This stunning home is ready to move in. Whether you are looking for a winter home, a first home, or a furnished rental, this is it. Maintenance free tropical living.
